1. *Puta* je bila duga. (The road was long.)
2. *Puta* se sastoji od tri dela. (The road consists of three parts.)
3. Prešli smo mnogo *puta* u poslednje tri godine. (We have traveled many times in the last three years.)
4. Ona je učinila grešku više *puta*. (She made a mistake more times.)
5. *Puta* je puna zavoja. (The road is full of turns.)
6. Znala sam da ću se vratiti kući istim *putem*. (I knew I would return home by the same way.)
7. Osećala sam se uzbuđeno kada smo krenuli *putem*. (I felt excited when we started our journey.)
8. Nije bilo lako nadvladati *put*. (It wasn't easy to overcome the journey.)